But in Rio de Janeiro, we can observe the reverse process - quite a large number of Russians are flying the flags of other countries.
In each case, the history of citizenship change is different.
Some parents took to another country as a child, leaving no choice.
Someone could not stand the competition for a place in the Russian team.
And someone believed that the best conditions for development in sports will be created abroad.
