Notifications for the transport tax will cease to be sent by mail - website Behind the wheel www.zr.ru
The tax inspectorate has changed the procedure for sending notifications about property taxes.
All Russian car owners are accustomed to the scheme that has not changed for years: in the summer and autumn, they receive mail receipts for the payment of transport tax for the previous year.
However, many will not wait for them this year.
The fact is that the tax inspectorate without too much noise changed the procedure for notifying citizens.
Those who are registered in the "Personal Cabinet of the taxpayer" on the official website of the department nalog.ru, the notifications will be submitted in electronic form.
The inspection automatically considered such Russians online users and erased them from the standard, "paper" mailing.
The innovation will affect all owners of vehicles and real estate.
All others will still receive the usual letters.
However, the owners of the account on the site also have the opportunity to return to the old scheme.
To do this, they will have to visit the department of the tax service during August and write a statement.
On the one hand, the new order is more modern and more convenient.
The notification will appear in the "personal office" immediately after the preparation, while the letter will go a few days and may get lost.
In addition, the number of users of the Internet service of the tax inspectorate exceeded 18 million people, which will allow the department to seriously save on mailing.
On the other hand, the modest news on the inspection website is clearly not enough to inform citizens about the changed order.
Some could have registered in a "personal office" to get a one-time service and have long forgotten about it.
These people will not wait for the notifications by mail and, without knowing it, will fall into the category of defaulters with all the ensuing consequences.
Access to the "Personal Cabinet of the taxpayer" is carried out in three ways: through the account of the portal gosuslugi.ru, using an electronic signature or entering the login and password specified in the registration card.
The latter can be obtained personally at any department of the tax inspectorate (regardless of the place of registration).
We remind you that this year the transport tax must be paid before December 1.
The notifications began in July.
